    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, presented in museum-quality condition. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a fully overhauled double-VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline remains reliably accessible. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis is structurally pristine with documented subframe reinforcement already performed. The suspension retains its factory-specified kinematics, complemented by fresh bushings and dampers for razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in original factory paint with zero oxidation, and an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this is a mechanically transparent specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
